dll.o:
gcc -c dll.c -o dll.o

dll_util.o:
gcc -c dll_util.c -o dll_util.o

For Static library:
ar rs libdll.a dll.o dll_util.o
-------------------
dll.o:
gcc -c -fPIC dll.c -o dll.o
similarly for dll_util.o

for dynamic library:
gcc dll.o dll_util.o -shared -o libdll.so
------------------------------
Static exe:
gcc -c application.c -o application.o
gcc application.o -o exesta -L . -ldll
usage: ./exesta

dynamic exe:
gcc -c application.c -o application.o
Place the libdll dynamic shared file in /usr/local/lib
i.e. sudo cp libdll.so /usr/local/lib
run sudo ldconfig
gcc application.o -o exedyn -ldll
usage: ./exedyn

